ed him down with them, he says - he brought - brought him - gave him to speak then, he was able to speak, he couldn't speak. So - it - he - he says you don't do anything more just now, he said, we'll just get you home. They got him home. It was a strained
 heart, he strained his heart, that was what the doctor said. He said he had strained his - \{BLANK\}
 That was a good wee bit from Moniaive you see, and - and - while he was there of course when - when the shooting time is - come - came in - they had a car yo
u see, and - and then he used to run his two things you see. You know, at - at - at Moniaive like, from the house if there was anything special on. Used to take us out you see, like that.
