orridge and - and then - fry a fry after. Mother was a great baker of - of potato scones, you know, oatmeal scones and - and - and flour scones - flour scone.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did she bake on a girdle or did she have an oven?
