e. She - she had the oven too on this range you see, but - she used to keep things hot in it, she - she didnae do so much in the - on the - she - mostly the girdle she was baking with. She - she - she - she did - she liked the plain sort of scones you kno
w
, and then she had a - a hanging oven, what you call a hanging oven, you know, the - that's - that's just like a - an ordinary pot but a - different shapes - different shape they are. And then - she used - she hang - she used to hang it on to cook, she wa
nted to cook - they had hooks in -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Up above the fire?
