\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11414884\charrsid5586003 That's - aye, oh}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003  dear, she ma
de many a good feed in - so honestly she - and - and she used to - just peep in you see to lift the tins and - and peep in to see if they werena getting too burned - too hot or that. And I mind many a good feed - bannock she made.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did she ever make bread?
