aybe - that you got the bread when the grocer came. When the grocer came with the order, and that, but - but she - she made do you see with - with - we - with having the - stuff that she made too as well you see. She did a lot of baking. She did a lot of 
baking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did she make jam as well?
