\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11414884\charrsid5586003 With a lot of fruit in i}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 t?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye. Yes. Blackcurrant bushes and gooseberry bushes and - and plenty of rhubarb and - all the things - just - just right. S
he made the jam. Of course you see - things was cheaper then you see, in - in - and she always kept plenty of sugar in. She made the jam and the - curd, and - have -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Enough to keep you through the winter?
