\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You would grow enough potatoes to keep the family over the winter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Y
es, we just kept ourself going well. And - and then - they - if they were needing anything extra - she - she just told the grocer like, we was three miles off Sanquhar were the town you see, where the - the grocer's place was. - But he come this - come up
 on the - on - with the order, and then if there was anything else or extra - she - she - she put in - they would deliver them again, come a special journey - and deliver them. And then of course we had to get our coals from the pit.
