\insrsid11414884\charrsid5586003 u}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 ldnae get the peats to work out you know. The peats had - the peats had to be - nice and dry for - for kindling - for kindli
ng up, and then - there was - there was - some - it was larger - you - mother used to bank the fire with them you know like that.
