- the - the - we were all out at that job, the - the - the - my father had a - we were all out at that job, there was a big peat moss - one of the - one of the fields - that was away low down, and you just called it the peat moss you see because it was th
e kind of - stuff for the peats and - and then - there were - like the father and the young herd and - then the boys, the two boys helped us do it.
