rt. Aye, there was a stable - you see, outside in the close - there was a stable, and - and - then there was the - big byre. There was the big byre for the - was - where - mother - looked after cattle - for them, for byre - our own cows, she had her own c
ows as well. And - and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 I don't know where she found the time to do it all.
