 that you see like - and there was - that was - there - I think a Mr Goorlie - Goorlie I think they called him was - was their master you see, and there was a - a lead - a big lead - what they called the lead, of water - divided the - the fields. Aye. Jus
t off the - off the road - where there Geddes left on one side, and Hamilton on the other, and that was our neighbours like, mother}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11414884\charrsid5586003  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
