 stomach that wasnae very good, but she had a daughter and - and she used to come and - and see mother and that and - and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did she ever take you out visiting with her when you were wee?
