ed to - used to go there -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 What sort of bus was it, was it a horse bus?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No.
