ir, go down with bits of turns on - on - oh the - place - sands in Dumfries was crowded then you know from top to bottom. Far different now than what it is - and - and there was wee - wee horses you know and - all like that you could - could always - go o
n the horses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 That would be quite an exciting time for you then?
