Quite - quite - it was quite exciting for us see. So we was - well she never - she nev - she never went away without us you know, she - she just - took them away along, took us away
 along and then you had a - you had your dinner - dinner in - in the town, get it in - it was in the sands, it was in - the Vennel then where McKie's the restaurant was, McKie's restaurant it was, oh they were great old fold, we - you know, have - and tha
t was where we could go to - to - to get our dinner.
