 she left - the - the - Sanquhar school - for to - take up dressmaking, she wanted to learn the dressmaking. And - and things like that she - so they - I just - you know, carried on myself like. And - oh I was there - I think it was fifteen - I was fiftee
n before I left the school there. Yes.
