, they used to give us the - cards home with us you know, what they call cards with - with our things and that was homework, and we'd to do that at night. So I did - I never got right the - minding at all for that, I said I didn't understand the cards I u
sed to say because I went home I was - I used to be helping mother you know with bits of things you see.
