then, he's a very funny old body the one that taught us in standard five, a Mr. Salmon, and - and he - oh he used - he was pretty strict too but he - he used to tell bits of stories and - and - he - he - like that, a good - we got on no so bad with him, h
e was kind enough you know. And if we were wet - go - going in - he - he made us - change our stockings and - change our - take off our boots and our stockings, get them dried.
