\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Yes. Yes. We had good - good strong - strong leather lacing boots like for the - for this ground, see. Rough ground.
