\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you get music at the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Singing, aye, we got singing lessons. Singing lessons and - and - in both of the - aye, both of the classes and sewing, sewing classes we had too. The sew - the sewing mistress was a - a - a Miss Clennell and she had one of the teachers for 
an assistant used to come in and help. And - and help us. To cut it out, the cloth, you had cloth to cut it out, and - and we had sewing then you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 What sort of things did you make?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 I - I - I made a nightdress once. You - you see - and - and 
- just useful things for - for - and - and - they - they taught us to - to do - you know, flowering - flowering, you know, what they used to call flowering, that was -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Decoration round the edges?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Yes, you know the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Is that broderie Angliase?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
I - I think so, you know, it was - you just aye call it flowering it, it was - it was a certain - no - no just like lace but - it was like done in - and it was done on the edges for - for nightdresses sometimes you see and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 There'd be a lot of work in that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
She taught us you see. And - she - she was - she - she was a - a - she was a friend of - of Mr Carson's, they - she was away before I left the school I think. Before I left there. Yes, she was - she was awful kind and - to show us a
nd she says if you - oh. She says, you'll no be a mother if you don't have plenty of pins sticking about you. She used to tell you know. And so -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you like singing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Oh yes, I liked singing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you have any musical instruments in the house at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Well no, not in our own house, no, not in our own home, just a fiddle. A fid - aye, the fiddle. It used to - hang up - in - up on the wall, and - and there was a cousin - a cousin used to come and he was a - a player, and it was grand, we 
used to like to hear him playing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 But none of your own folk played it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
No, no, well my father used to - take it down off the wall and - and - and - fiddle away to it but I mean he wasnae like - taught like to fiddle it. But if anybody - come in that was a fiddler he - he just got - the - the - the fiddle to play.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you ever sort of sing together as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Sing - singing? Aye, well if there only - only old songs and - and - joining in the chorus and - and that - and that. Mother wa
s a great admirer of Bruns - and he - she got all these - things. She just - well you see we was eleven years up in Carco cottage you see up at - so that mother - she says - folk used to say to her, are you no lonely and that and don't know what you do fo
r fun, well we can make our own fun, like that, she said, you can make her ain fun, and then she -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 What sort of things did you do then, like singing, did you do other things too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Like - when we were at home? No, just helping them - helping - wit
h the sheep like if it was a busy time I used to help my father. Like when - when we were on school holidays - we used to - help them. 'Cos my sister - she was at - the dressmaking you see, and - and that took her all day. She - she learned - she - she wa
s taught with a - a Miss Wilson.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Your mother said you made your own fun altho}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9984110\charrsid5586003 ugh it was lonely, I was wonder}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 ing what you did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye, well - I - ayes, well we just - we just - be singing and - and - and playing and maybe hiding a wee bit there to wi
th the - with some of the rest of the - the shepherds boys, or - or - or the - ones - or the ploughmen. The ploughman was - was like across the close you see, the - we - we - we got a - the - there - there were - where we lived in was long like that and -
 
and anyway just across from it - across was where the - the - ploughman, the - he had a helper too but that was where he lived you see, and I think we went - the one that used to help him - was like a young fellow, he was up in the farm house. Farmhouse w
as away up the road a bit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 So there were always children for you to play with if you had spare time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye, there'd be - we had our wee bits of - our - our concerts and - and - and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you get parties for birthdays at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Wee bits of 
parties. Wee bit of birthday parties, see. See she - now - no very far - we went up - went up to the other shepherd's house too, and he was a kind of comical body, he could - he could - recite and - and make - and - and play the violin too, he had a violi
n and - and he had his family about - about him like that And - and the - and the dumplings - the making of the dumplings was a great go then you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 This was for your birthday was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye - making a big dumpling, a - a clootie dumpling you ken.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 With fruit in it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Aye. Mother had a - she had a good big - big pot - that she - I don't know how she lifted the thing, she - but - after I got on a bit I left - I - I - lifted them off the fire, and - and they were heavy. But she - she - this 
what she did, she mixed this big clootie dumpling. And - and - and it was - fixed up and - this - this pot was hanging on the - on the hook, and - had to - over an hour it was kind of - starting to boil and - and in went the dumpling. And then - she had a
lways to - to keep it boiling you see. Maybe be about two - two hours or more you see, it was a good size - 'cos they were all - it was full of - full of - fruit you see. And -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did she keep a special cloth for making it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye. Aye, yes, a strong 
cloth. A strong cloth that - that - that she - that - then she spread it out and put flour - on it - in it, and emptied out the - the - mixture, the dumpling - and then - tied it all up you see, like - left - left - left room a wee bit to swell you see. A
nd she popped it into the - into the pot to - and then she used to keep her eye on it you see after that no to let it get boil it dry you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 So that was what you got for birthdays then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 That is it. And - and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you get presents at a birthday or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No - like we just - just sort of - get a wee bit extra - something in the - like cake and a wee bit extra meal and that, you know, just -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 What about Christmas time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Oh we all. -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you get presents then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 We always got something in your stockings on Christmas Day. It was a great go - han}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9984110\charrsid5586003 g}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 ing up our stockings you know. And then you always got -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Where did you hang your stocking up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 At the back - at the bed side.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You took yours to bed with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Foot of the bed, aye. It was - oh it was a great fun to - like - these -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 What would you get in your stocking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Oh just - just a lot of - you know like - we always had a big - we had had - shortbread and - home made shortbread - and - and - and cake
s or - and then - ribbon for our hair or - and - lots of things you know just that was - that you was - certain things you was needing you know. We always wore our - our hair long you see and - and - the bow - bows of ribbon you ken, was tied back - at - 
at the back with bows of ribbon.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You made quite a thing of Christmas then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Aye, they - they all kept - we all kept it up you see that way, we just all had a wee bit - bit - bit tea, you know, with some of the neighbours you ken coming in and - and your neighbours' family and that, just a week bit happy night just amongst them.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 How about New Year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Oh aye, we used to say -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you have first footing and things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye, they - they all gathered you know, the - all someone come in 
late you know in New Year night and - and - we had a wee bit the same sing-songs and - and - and that, it was grand. A wee bit dance on the flag - flag floors there were. But mother had - rugs and - and that she laid out. Home made rugs she - you know the
 - she used to do - make her own rugs, rag rugs. There's none of that now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Was there any drinking at Christmas or New Year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Any what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Drinking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Drinking, oh aye, they - they did - they - they could - well, whisky was on the go you know
. But - the - it - it was chiefly tea you know, I mean it was tea - after that, tea to the dumpling and - and - and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 What did your mother and father think about drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Oh they - my father - my father took whisky you see, mother didnae drink
, mother didnae drink, she's - she's - she was very good at - at having it in the house if there were anything went wrong with us, when was away you see. When - when when was - anything was ill or that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 But she didn't take any herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No, she -
 oh no, she was sober. She was - she was - she was really a good manager my mother, she - she left my father - to - to all his own - own kind of work, you know, the shepherding and - and - and the working like that. But if there were anything went wrong w
i
th the lambs - it was - just bring them in to the fire, you know. And - and - and - and - they were - all - fed and sorted up and - laid on the rugs at the fire, the lambs. And in no time too they were dancing round about on the floor. For while - while -
 whiles they did - if they were kind of - far through - whiles they did get a wee bit teaspoonful of - of whisky, sometimes you know for a - for them - to help them on.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 To revive them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye, to revive them. Oh it - it helped many a one that was weakly. Yes, it used to grand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Your mother wouldn't have a great deal of time for reading, did she read anything at all, did she have any books or magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No. But got the papers. We got aye the papers see, see the grocer brought the papers up,
 and then the Standard too, always kept on - on with the Standard you see, and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you get a paper every day then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No, no, no, no}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9984110\charrsid5586003 t }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 every day. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Just when the grocers van came up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye, grocers van brought up the papers for us. And 
then there was a postman you see come up too, the postman would come along you see, and - and got - got the stick up - if we had any letters to post - we'd to stick them up on the window, and - and you see when he was coming up the road, he could see them
, and he - and he'd come up to the door to get them, but - if there nae - nae sign of anything he - he kenned there wouldna be anything. It was three mile for the postman as well you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Would he come out if he didn't have any letters to deliver, would he still come out to see if there were any letters to go back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No, oh no, oh he - they delivered letters if they had any letters and that. Come up with them you see just to see them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 But would he come up whether he had letters to deliver or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Like he - he come up if he saw the - them sticking on the window - you see. That's what they - they - whet he called the signs, if there's any to post, he says, just put them up you see - in the window, he says, I'll know, he says, I'll come up fo
r them. And he got always correspondence away. Oh they were very good. And then you had - I don't know this - we'd always to go that three mile - to Sanquhar you see - to the Post Office. If thedre were anything went wrong with the cattle. There's once th
