re were a - one of mother's cows took milk fever, milk fever you see, she was awful grandmilker, but she - she took this milk fever, and - I mind I was - I was at home at the time just - and I happened to have my - my new bicycle. So - she - she said go d
o
wn with that - milk fever you see to - the - so the cow went down with it and - and - and so - we had to go to the - to have - to bring the vet you see. Like you hadnae a phone or anything in the house of that you see. So when - when - I got onto my bicyc
