\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Who all came to it, just all the shepherds from round about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 The shepherds, the shepherds you see. And then - some of their - t
he young - the young shepherds - if there were a lot of them - employed young shepherds, they - they were on the go too you see, they came in and - and - they were all players and singers a lot amongst them. And dancers, liked a bit dance. We just watched
 them you see, then, because we were just at the school you see. But -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Were there any other schoolchildren near you to play with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No. No, no, just at - just at the school, just at - Craigmoy school. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 So you just had your sister and your two cousins to play with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Yes, that's it, just - we - we - went when they were here. Of course the boys - the boys were - left the school you see, they werenae at the Craigmoy school. Just my sister and I.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 How is your cousins come to stay with you in the first place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
My two cousins? Their - their - a sister of my father's - was the mother - were their mother. A sis - a sister of my - and she wasn't married you see, and - and - and the two - the two boys - she was working, she was out worki
ng - but - the - the two boys you see was left with the old people, the - that's - that's my grandfather and my grandmother, well - it was too much for - too much for my grandmother you see, to bring them forward you see, because she had - she'd her own f
a
mily too as well you see, some of the younger ones anyway, the younger family, they were all out working as they got forward you see. But - the - we just made our own fun you know and - and - and - in - in the winter nights especially I mean you - played 
maybe a - a - a game - a game at the cards, maybe - Old Miad or - or catch the tail or something like that you know just - for - and we used to get my father - if he - if he wasnae going out anywhere we used to get him in - interested init too you see.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 He used to play with you sometimes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Yes. And mother and all took a hand sometimes. And then - the - Robert was a great one - for - you - you -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 If your father wasn't going out somewhere he would take a hand at cards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye, he'd take a - if he wasna going - well he never was out in the evenings much but -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12147710\charrsid5586003  if he was working late - among}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003  his sheep or anything like that you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 But he didn't go out very much to enjoy himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No. No unless it was - unless he was away at a sale or any
thing where they - with the sheep or cattle. Yes, you see - he had to be - forward at the marts and that you see to - see them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 What sort of games did you play when you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Well -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 When you did have some company to play with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Well you - you - you know, just - hide and seek was one of them I think you know, and and just - sort of - tig you know, it was only a wee place, there wasnae much - wasnae man - many outdoor parts in it, it was just a - the - it would - the - the teac
her just lived as - at - at the - one of the endsof the school you see, this - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 So there wasn't much scope for games,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No, there wasnae much scope you see, we had to - we had to have our scope walking towards the - the school - back and forwa
rd to the school, aye. Well the - the rest of them - had - you know, had long journeys too some of them, coming - coming over - get - some of them had to come over the hills you see, but then - they were - older than us lot again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 So you wouldn't be able to join any youth organizations, you wouldn't be able to join any clubs or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
No, no, we didnae join anything like - anything at all. You see just when you went - just - it was my sister - when - when you went up - Crawick Glen y
ou see, she - she joined in - into regular in the dressmaking. She was left the school then you see. She left the school before me, I went on 'til I was fifteen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 I think you said you had people to play with when you were up at Carco?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Yes. There 
were - there were - family - the family across the - the closes you see, there was the - was the - was the foreman - ploughman's - daughters and that, when they were at the school, they went to the school, all went to school together down the three mile y
o
u see, and then - further up the road was the other shepherd, the other married shepherd and - and - and he had a son that wasnae at - wasnae - left the school, and he joined us too. He - got forward - in - in his life and he's - I - I don't know where he
 
lives now, where about Gretna or somewhere, but he got to be awful clever. Clever fellow he was. And - and he was on the police - he was on the police here too like in Dumfries. He was - he was on - for a while on - in traffic - traffic warden and that. O
h he was - and then - they were at my husband's funeral, I met him there again. Aye. You see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you have sprees when you were at Carco?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Yes, often. Often you know just - there was - always - you'd always wee parties you know, just amongst ourse
lf. And - and - visiting - visiting others - shepherds' houses and - they came to my mother's you see. They came to ours. And - then mother always made a big dumpling. It was a big dumpling and - and she'd cut it out and dished it on - in our - in our tea
, and the dumpling and - that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You seem to have had a good time even though you were out in the country?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Oh it was - it was fine, it was - you know that there were - there were nobody interfered - we - we had the room in the kitchen - but after 
it was repaired it was - it was big enough you know, it was good and then there was a wee bit - just - just near the door where - where it was - it was where the - the - the water - had to sit you know, we had to bring the water - round - there were a big
 boiler - round again at the byre you know, fresh running water you know into - and then mother - brought - brought some of her cans and brought them into - this wee bit at the door. She had them on shelves and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You didn't have running water there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
No, not inside, we'd no - we'd no - nothing inside for - for - for convenience. It was just at this - there was this big - boiler. It kept this running water. It was coming from a spring, and it - and it was always running you see, so - so -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 So it would be nice and fresh?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Oh yes, we always got it - and then of course it had to do for the - for the - for - for the cattle as well you see, and - and - it - really for lots of things. See, this was handy at the byre. And then often after when 
they - tidied up the - the byre, she used to when - she used to clean the boiler out you see too - for - when she wasnae needing it for much, and - and - wash - wash out the - the pails, you know, wash out the byres, you know, the - after they were cleane
d down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Just another of the jobs that she had to do. Did you ever have to help carrying the water?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Aye. Oh it wasnae - it wasnae far to carry the water, it was just at the - at the - the - the door, there were - like there was like two doors in t
he byre you see, and it was at that end, where the boiler was and it was quite handy you see to lift it out you see. And then she had - we had - the big house was in - in the close too, and - and you always - mother always kept the two pigs - two pigs and
 
fattened them up. My goodness, she did - she did - she was good to them, and - and she - you see she used to go into - when - when the garden - was good and - and she used to go into them and - they knew her you know they had - she was - she passed by the
 
- the pig house you see, to go into the - to this garden, and she just spoke if they were - if they werenae sleeping she - she would have spoke to them, and when she come back she threw some - cabbage blades or something like that - over into them you see
, she often was giving them something, you see, like that. She - fed them up you know that and she used to - when it comes to the parting of the ways she just felt it. She felt it you see. But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You've got to be hard hearted about these things haven't you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Aye, that's true, oh yes. But - but - you see the - as - as the years went on - it got more and more done with the butchers and butchers come up from Sanquhar into the field and - you know, and - and it was all over just in the shortest of noti
ce, you see, the old - the old ways, it was - it was - they had to - boil water you know and - and scrape them, you see, scrape the - the pigs after they were killed like. But - but they new method - was - the - they skinned them, you see, they - they - t
h
ey - the butchers from Sanquhar. So you see mother hadna - mother hadnae - it was just - it was just come - the - don't boil any water or anything for us Mrs Swan, he says, we'll - we'll have a - this old boy - and - in no time. And so they had. And then 
you see there was - I think there was three of them come, I - I - I think there was three like, there was - there was - Grays the butchers you see and he had - his assistants with him you see too. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 When they came did you want to see what they were doing or did you keep out of the way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Well - we could see on the close like we could see through the door of course but we never - we never liked to see them - getting killed either you see. She was - she was working and feeding them and - keeping them clean and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 When you were little did you ever get to any concerts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Concerts in Sanquhar. If - if there were any - if there were any big concerts on in Sanquhar hall - when they - they had - they had a hall - any - I used to come down. Use
d to come down, there were - and there were sometimes - there were plays on, plays on you see. The - my father - we used to get my father to come but my sister and I used to go - down there. In that hall, it - it's -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did your mother not come?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No, she kept the house and - when - and the dogs was what - she'd always a dog.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 So she had to stay behind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
She - and - and then - Robert, he wasnae away then, that's the - that was - the younger cousin. He went to Canada in - in - in - latter years. But - he used to stay - he used to stay with mother for company and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 So you got off with your father to the plays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye. And - 'course we - it - it was a good bit to walk after the show was finished you see and that. And then he went to s
hows too you know, the - cattle shows you know. Went out to the cattle shows.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 What was it like going there?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You see the - we had Thorn - we'd have Thornhill one - and - and then you would - we had a show in about Sanquhar too. But - the Thronhi
ll one you see - we had our - had a dog that - a collie dog at - at the sheepdog - show - showed the collie dog. But she was up - up for show, but she - she - she got third, she did fine. Collie.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did they have to work with the sheep in the competitions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
No, no. It was just - aye, it was just - there for show you see. And then - could walked round and - and - and - see - with having the dog you see we got in for nothing you see, with having a dog at the show. And - and then - of course we - we tra
velled - I think we travelled - back - we must have got a lift back I think at that time. The whole lot of us. And the - they had - the - there was always - we were always meetings friends too at the show you see, and then - we got to - got - some tea or 
something like that before - before we finished up. Oh if it was a good day, it was quite a nice - turn out, really always a nice turn out at Thornhill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did they have entertainments at the shows in those days like they do now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No. No - they - the
re - there were - there was - the Rood Fair here, you know, like the - the - there's the - well, the March Fair will be soon coming on you see and shows come in for that you know, the shows, the - the - but - and it's all about and - and - and you went up
 
to a - some - kind of show I think it was, and - at Thornhill, and then at night - there - there was a - a place where the - there was shows come in you know, just you know - for a time. But you got - we got - we got a lift back and forward with the motor
s or - wasnae so bad like - down to Dumfries. Of course I was grown up then you see. Bit older.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 When you were at school did you get any pocket money or did you just get some money to spend if there was something special on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No. Yes, we didnae get
 - get money to spend much you see - but - if we - had - had nae a big enough piece with us - mother - always got - mother always gave us something and then - she could buy - you could buy down shop, in shopping, something to eat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you ever get away for holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No. Well - no, no unless it was just to see - our own people like - the - to - to visit our own - folk, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You went away occasionally to visit some relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye, that's it you see. And - and - mother - mother would
 - they would travel down you see. Had to travel down - from Sanquhar you see, down to Dumfries - for to - to find out - mother's - mother's father - mother's mother and - and - down about Ruthwell. They were at Howthwaite Cottage, Ruthwell there, and - a
n
d then - then when - when she was a widow - she - they came - came to live at Carrutherstown Carrutherstown, that's at - aye, aye. So you see she - oh she was a big tall - fine looking woman, but - she - my - mother's mother. She had a hard life after her
 husband died. You see, he died -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you go and stay with her when you were little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No, went often to see them like you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You'd just go down for the day would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye. Just used to go down for the day or that. 'Cos you could take
 the train once you got to Dumfries you could - we could take the train down you see, it wasnae that far and it wasnae that far, Carruthertown for the station, or for the - or for the Howthwaite - Howthwaite cottage where she was, it wasnae far to walk.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you ever}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12147710\charrsid5586003  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
visit any of your father's relations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
My father - my father - aye, they were at - they were at - they were at Tinwald you see, at Tinwald - you see, we had to come down - we had to come down to Dumfries - you see, and then - make out 
- make - make out to Tinwald - but - but no when - now when you was grown up you see, that was - that was - just on our school holidays or that and mother used to come with us, and visit them you see, visit the - the - the -
