 a place they called the orchard - further down - further down the road, this was from Carco, down the road and I - and - her husband - it - it was the mother that was - that was connected with mother. And - and - Crichton was their name - but he was - th
e
y were a great big tall men, but they were drainers, you know, the - the - him and his sons, the - the father and the sons, they were drainers that took on contracts you know and all different contracts, and they were drainers. Aye they were clever - and 
