\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No, I don't think she ever had a job, she just - she was - she - she - there's a
 sister - I mean - of Mr Robinson's - lived in Terregles Street and she - she was supposed to be - going blind. She used to come up and see her - and when she - called her auntie you see, and - and I got always auntie - to take home at night you see. She 
was a great old soul, and - but - as soon as she got out in at the door now sit down, just you sit down and put your feet up. She said. She was awful kind. Kind to me. 'Cos it - it was what - you see, they wanted to see her home you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Make sure she got home safe?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Yes, got home safe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 And it wouldn't be}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12147710\charrsid5586003  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 all that far?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 It wasnae that far, coming down Laouriknowe Avenue you see and just turning in - to Terregles Street and she was just there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 How did you get on with Mrs Robinson? What sort of person was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Well - the - the - the mother, like the missus - oh she was quite easy - easy to do, she was - she was a kindly person she was. Aye, she - she'd - she never - interfered with me in anything you see. She -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 What did she do with her time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Oh she - she did - she wasna very - sometimes she wasnae very grand you know I think she -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Her health wasn't very good?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye, she got took in for something - I don't know what really it was but she - there was - oh - a nurs
e came and - and sort of gave her - treatment in the house, just at different times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did she go out a lot or was she tied to the house?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No, she would - they wore - they - they held - what you call - days, you know, name days, you know, for - fo
r - having their - visitors coming, you know, specially, holding the - the - well this is my day sort of style you know and - and they came all from the different houses, and then of course she would be back when it was her turn to go to them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 What sort of people came to visit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Well just the local - well, the - the - the - the ones that was - well they were - some of them was neighbours do - do you see, in Victoria - Victoria Road, and then - there was other ones - there was the - there was some of the Barbours - Barbours.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 That's a shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Yes, that's a shop kind, Barbours. And - and there was shortages too you see, the Shortages.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 At the laundry is that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye, the laundry, you see they were well up - they were well up too up see
 the Shrtages, because they had - they had - a good business then you see that Mills is running - and that. And they used to come and - and then of course the - the - the young - the - the family, this - young - young sons - and then they were golfers too
 you see and and then they had their friends coming in at different times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You would be kept busy then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye with the different - aye, we had to have a wee bit extra on - bit - bit extra meal you see for them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Mr Robinson wouldn't be at home when you had the at homes would he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No, he would just -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 That would just be for the ladies would it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
It's just for the ladies, afternoon tea and - and - and that, they - no, they were - he had his office, Mr Robinson - Robinson, and then yo
u see his sons were - in - in solicitors offices too I think. I think there was - I think there would be - I think the eldest son if I can mind right, was in his office, was in the father's office, and then - the other ones - there was other - other two -
 and there was one, a - Charlie - Charlie they called him, he - I don't remember him you see, he was away, but he was away abroad in \{BLANK\} So he - oh they were dis - you know, they just sort of married }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12147710\charrsid5586003 through-}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 hither through times you know, the - people that they knew you see too, were friendly. Yes. That's right, yes, that's right.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did they do any entertaining at night when Mr Robinson was there, did they have dinner parties at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No. No, no really, no they were - it was just I think befor
e - before - Elsie they called her got married you see, Miss Elsie. She was - fair - fair hair, she had fair skin.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 A pretty girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye, she was quite nice and - and - and high colour, she had always a high colour. 'Cos - so ex - just a wee bit ex
tra meal you know if - they gathered any in and - and Doctor Dykes was - coming too you see, always there you see. And it had to be - had to attend to him you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 What about when you got some time off, did you get off at nights there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No, like 
- I did - well a day off if we want it, you see, or going out a turn but - I - I didnae bother going very far you see because - I - I used an odd time - went to some friends you know, at - just - at nights you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You just went visiting friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye, just like - you got to know by being at the church maybe or something like that you see. And - and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You kept going to the church regularly when you came to Dumfries did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Yes, we used to go to - evening services mostly it was you see because you were sort of free then you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Was it Laurieknowe you went to as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Oh yes, but - there was two you see, there was - that was the - what you'd call the old church Laurieknowe and it was - it was a Revered Mr Slesser then, it - th
at was the minister. And then - just - just further - just further down - near the - near the bottom - was the - Mr - it's Mr Simmons's now - but he was - it was a different - minister then of course, but - Mr Simmons's, it was more of a Free Church - Fre
e - what they called a Free Church. It was very nice so we - used to go there of an evening to you see because - hear the preach - hear the different preachers. But - hymn books was different you see, the hymn - yes, being a Free Church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you go out with the cook to these things or did you have other friends that you went with?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Oh sometimes - sometimes we went together, Maggie and that, but - but then - and - and other times you - were just - maybe didna have the same night off or that. She we
nt to - have her own friends. Of course she had more experience in - in - in - that kind of work because I was just seventeen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you find it a bit lonely then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Being in the town having lived in the country all your life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No - no
 too lonely, but - I think it was I just homesick or something, I got homesick But - there - there were some - there some - some of the McMillans - well - they were far out connections of my father's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Is that the ones that you used to get your dinner with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Aye, in - yes, well this was a brother, this - this John McMillan - was a brother of the ones that was the clogger in Sanquhar - so - he used to meet - he was a tailor too for them, he was the tailor for the - for Mr Robinson, and his sons, and - and -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 So you would be able to go and visit them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 That was - down the road. They were just above - used to be Chickens the bakers, it's away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 So the McMillans stayed near the bakers did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye, they - that - that was a - above ch
ickens, they - they lived - on the flat above chickens the bakers, so they were fine and handy for - for going or anything. But the - they didnae - I mean they didnae have the - the - the cottage loafs or anything that - you wanted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you manage to make any friends apart from the girl you worked with and the McMillans?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
The - well there were - just - it would be through the church you see, the - they were - friends that you - through met anyway do you see and went to their house, like when you w
ent to their house like it was often the Sunday night, after the church, after we'd been to church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You would go home with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Went to their house. But it was never very far and wasnae out of the town or anything that way.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you ever go to dances or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
No, then - no then, but - as - as I got on - as I got on I got - tea - I got - Mary Carter, she's off - of course they're all away now but they Carters were all musical - musical family. And Mary Carter was the one 
that was the teacher, teaching you to dance and - and - and then we went to her classes. But however - I was - I left - I was a wee while away from Dumfries - and then you see I helped our father - I helped my mother when - when - when I was - when she - 
my father wasnae needing me you see, with - with the cattle and one thing and another and - but my father - you see he had busy time every year, the lambing time and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12147710\charrsid5586003 hewing}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 , and then if he was - and then when it comes on for the - the clipping time he was away at clippings too you see. They had - but - but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you come back to work in Dumfries after you'd been home for a while?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Yes. Came down to - there was a Mrs - there a Miss Lot - she - the - the house, it was Crawford Villa was the name of t
he place, it's - it's - it's no very far off - off St Michaels church manse. This is is - it was - there were two - it was a - a semi-detached villa, you know - there was - there was - she was Miss Watt and she just wanted - someone to help her like. See,
 and stay in the house with her. 'Cos she had her father and mother and they were elderly you see then. Mr Watt died when - while I was there with them. I was there a good wee while with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 More than a year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Oh yes. And then - we got - you kno
w, when you finished and the - it was kind of heavy place too, sometimes you got help in, but it - it was -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you have to do the cooking there too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Yes, it was just - help in the - in the - in the kitchen and - and - oh she - she did odd jobs 
too, Miss Watt you see, but she was a - her mother was a sort of invalid too. She was elderly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 She would have to spend a lot of her time looking after them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Yes, yes, looking after her, and then of course Mr Watt - he - he - he was a retired gen
tleman you see but he - he - he was elderly, but - he -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 What sort of job had he been doing before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Oh I think it would be - in - in - solicitors work or something. He was in some big shop - big - business or something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 An office or something?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Yes, like - because - he retired and - and then they were - they were sons - there - there was one - there was one a doctor, he was away - Doctor Watt, he was away, and his wife wasnae very strong either. And - and then there was another son - so
n - he was abroad - in some hot country, but he come - he come home once while I was there, and you know, he had - he had to shift his - his - boots - do you know what pile of boots you had to clean for him, and one day - you know, aye, he kept changing h
is boots. I don't know what it would be - whether it would be him coming from the hot country or no I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 He had bother with his feet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Something must have been for you see to - and - he particularly wanted them cleaned you know, shiny. He just -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 That was one of your jobs was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 That's one of my jobs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Was it a big house to keep, it wouldn't be as big as Beechcroft was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No, no, it wasnae as big as Beechcroft bu there was - there was - there was the big room down the
 stair and - and - and the big bedroom - upstairs like, it was up that direction, it was up a stair, and - and there were attic - there - there were - an attic - they would be attic rooms now likely for it's been all changed you see, I often have a look a
long where I used to - tread about you know, coming off the road. Of course it's all changed you know - with buildings you know and different houses and that, and -
