\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye, like - she had - Bessie of c
ourse is - she had - when it come near the time for my father - you see, when - when he took - you see - at the big clippings and things like that you see mother had to - had to - row the wool, the - you know it was all done with the shears then, the clip
p
ers you ken, and - and - be big bags hanging up you know to fill - with the fleeces in, and she wore a - she had a fleect - or a fleece and she was - she was one of them that was - rowing up the wool. Goodness knows when I look back and think I see her - 
she - she was - she - like a young body and she wasnae you see, you see she was getting on for - middle age then you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 She could turn her hand to anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 She - she could - she - she had to start - work whenever her father died you see, when 
ever her father died she - she - there was a - it was a big family of them you see. So - she went out - she went - she went on with it to help - help her mother. She was - she - oh she was a hard worker, and just seemed to - fit in, she just seemed to fit
 in with everything, you know, this - in life somehow as I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 But she enjoyed her life too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 And they had their parties that you talked about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Oh yes, she - oh yes, she enjoyed her life. She - she liked it - she liked her fun. You k
now - just - this now - so very long ago, that was before I took the - the - the chill and that with the - with the house have in - in - Grayson Avenue, it was a top flat, like I happened to be out - at the - at the gate. I don't know now what I was waiti
n
g on, but there was a - a fellow jumped off his bicycle, he says, and - he says, you'll no - you'll no know me he says, Mrs Sharp, but he says, I know you and I remember your mother, she was an awful cheery body, he said. They were Tinwald folk, he had hi
s father was in - it was Wilson they called him. Scott Wilson. So - so -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Your mother was well known and well liked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Was well liked, aye. She was awful well liked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Were either your mother or your father interested in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 They - oh they were - they go to vote and one thing and another, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Who would they vote for do you think? What were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Oh - Liberals in that days, Liberals - aye, they - they - they were mostly Liberals you see, the - that - they were taking a kind
 of lead in that - at that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 What about you when you were old enough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Oh it - I was - just - had to go with the - go - go with the ones that was - sort of serve with you know - I - I think so, to - to - help them or something that way. You know, in the - it was -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You mean they actually said to you how they should vote?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You just did it anyway?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 I just - just had to sort of go - go with - go with them you see, yes. 'Cos they liked you to - be the same, they wouldnae
 have liked you to be different you know with the - all had their own - but old Mrs - Miss Watt entertained a good bit too after - after the father died, and - and - and her brothers - used to come, and she had a sister - that - that was married on a Mini
s
ter, and they used to come and stay you see, and then - then there was always a wee bit extra on - then. Aye. Aye. In the house. But I - I got - a wee bit help from her then. And then - the - the - Mrs - Gould - Mrs Gould or something they called her, if 
e
ver Mr Gould I think was the name of the minister but they came for - for - Eastburn I think, Eastburn I think you see, and - and they stayed their holidays and - and she'd two daughters, and they liked to be coming in and - and - helping me in the kitche
n.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 How did you get on with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Oh - oh fine. Fine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 They were just young were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye, they were just young. And then - the - their mother - the mother helped too a wee bit with the cooking, used to have extra then.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 It's not so bad if there was extra work to be done and they were willing to help with it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
No. No. Well I hadnae the experience for to stop them you know what I mean. I did never interfere with any of them you see, coming and going in the kitchen or ocht like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did Miss Watt sort of let you get on with the work yourself or did she come and tell you what she wanted done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Well - it - it was just - oh she sort of - aye, in the - in the mornings you know, in the forenoon - she - she was mostly - helpi
ng you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 She would be working about with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Aye. Aye. And then I had the - had the bed - the bedrooms to do you know and that and a wee bit extra when it was cleaning time you see, there was always some}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6424897\charrsid5586003  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 boy - she did have a - a woman that come in too to help, and if she was going to be away anywhere - there was a woman came in to - to sort of help us you see and - and see that - things was going all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Do you remember what kind of pay you got there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Oh it was - I don't - don'
t know whether it was two pound a month or - or how it wrocht in, something like that, I know - it - it - the wages wasnae high but - I mean I - I was well fed so - and had a good comfortable bed and everything you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You were well fed there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Yes, they did - liked their food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Were you well fed at the Robinsons?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye. Oh aye, they were good, they liked their food, the whole lot of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You just got the same food as the family did you
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Yes. Aye, well - after we attended to th
em first and then after - we could sit down to a bite you see. Mag - Maggie and me - oh it was - two or three courses at the dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You talked about the gentry and yourselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Oh that was - that was -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 That was when you were very young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
At Lochur, aye, they were the gentry. Oh they had their own places and they brought their own maids - brought their own maids with them and their cooks and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 What would you say was the main difference between them and you though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Oh well
 - it was just a case that - they were from the English side you see, and - and - they - their - their friends - it was the shooting season that - that was the busy time you see. The - the old gentleman that took over - was a Mr Hepburn. Because it was - 
it - it was his - relations, relatives came through and - and - Pitlochry was - Hignets and - and - and - and - all the different - and then - Mrs Hepburn had - had her friends too you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you feel that they were very much different from you though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
No, they didnae make any difference at all. No, they just mixed in with - but - but Mary - Mary the cook as you call her, she - they made their own bed - their own bread. Aye. And - with the - with the peat fires you see, and - and - Mary - Mary -
 made the - the bread, and mother - mother - when she was kind of free handed she - she helped her and - and - and picked up the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 When you came to work in the town, you were working for -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Miss Watt.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Were they gentry as well, the Robinsons and the Watts would you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Well no, they were just - they were - they were in the offices you see and you had to sort of look up to them too you see because they - they had their - their offices you see, and then the house was their own - the - Bee
chcroft was their own like you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You felt that they were a bit better than you did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Ah well of course we - was just the maids you see. I was just a maid, the house table maid you see and - and my - Maggie was the cook you see. But I - I - that was just my first experience, and - in a town. That was my first experience you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you feel there was a big difference between the working people and the business people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye - you know they - they used to - oh they were good too at 
letting us out - we got out to - used to sort - sort of out and away to the - away to the fair and - one thing and the other.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 But the likes of the Robinsons wouldn't go to the fair would they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Oh - I don't know whether they went to the - they -
 they would - they'd walk through them like we had but I mean they didn't - aye, you see that was the days that the - that there was so many of them, so many of they shows in and - and that. They all got through. Oh they sort of patronized them you see. B
ut it's all different, it's different now you see, the - they don't get so long now. They - they - they - they don't, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you work anywhere else after that before you got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Yes. I - I - I left - Miss Watts and went away back up to Craw
ick Glen again to my mother - help my mother and my father. But - I got a - a - a - I took a job just temporary - for - at a farm - at a farmhouse because they had nae - they hadnae anyone for to help the - the cook when they - when they're baking and tha
t, they were - they - they - Mr Dalgleish - and his sons you see was there, he wasa widower, but - he - he was connected with the - with the Dickies too you see, and that's it - I went to them - I - I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Was that quite near your own home then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye
, well I had to cycle you see that was a wee bit - that - that was - down - the - the - you - Loch - the - the Euchan Road, the - you know, there was a - a road - cut off - the main road, and - and it was down there - where this farm was. Ulizie - Ulziesi
de, but on the way from there now you see the - family grew up and they scattered and then they lost a son - during the first world war, he was in the - in the - armoured car}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6424897\charrsid5586003 c}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 as}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6424897\charrsid5586003 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003  or something you see. Their eldest son. So -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You didn't stay there in the house for that, you just cycled back and forward to your work did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
No, I stayed - I stayed her - the time you see, just to help them 'til they got a - another - another girl - woman that could stay in, could - could be - back there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You didn't live in the house though did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
I - I stayed at night in the house, oh yes. Aye, because I had to be there - for the - making the food in the morning, getting the - the lads out you see. Big growing lads.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 You were a housekeeper really there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Aye, yes, baking just for a - a - a short time, I don't know whether - I managed for three month or no, I think I did - I think maybe I did you see but - it was awful difficult for to get the - the - the - the kind of - woman that they wanted, bec
ause she - they wanted one that could - could bake and - and wash and - and - and - and do all that sort of thing.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Somebody that would be a wife without -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Yes. Aye. And always tend to them. But I went home after - I went - I - I - they did come
 for me - I - I was twice there I think. They - they come for me - they - I don't know whether they made her run away or no or something but - they - they were without any help anyway, so I said I would just come like - just - you know for a short time, a
n
d - and he - he came up for me in the days that - that was the days of the pony and traps, you know, the - he hadnae his motor then and - but - they did get a lot of - we did get a motor - before I left one of the times. Oh they were quite nice, quite nic
e to - to serve for but I mean to say you needed to be strong to - to stick in and work for them, work. But I didna take on any milking or - or anything like that, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 But you enjoyed working there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Aye, I did - did baking - baked -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Were they friends of your before you went to work there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13568274 AS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 
Yes, we knew them like, we knew - we knew - we knew who they were like, they - the - the Dalgleishes, and - and then you see - my sister - was with - Mrs Dickie at the Tower was a - was a daughter, she
 was a daughter, a married daughter. Aye. You see. She was a mar - she was a married daughter you see, so that - we just - had her down sometimes you know just for a wee turn.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9461452 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9263038\charrsid5586003 Did you get much time off when you worked there?
