ister of my father's had this holding - this small holding at Tinwald, but she - she was wanting to give it up because she was too - too old you see, and - and - and she - she lost her son - it - it was - he was - work - working in Dumfries at an ironmong
e
rs shop and that but he wasnae awful strong either, but they're - they are buried in Tinwald with - with the two of them, aye, so we got - she - she wanted - my father to get that hold - get the holding, you see, aye, to - yes, to - keep it you see, it be
