onged to - Jordons - Jordons of the Jordon Hall - was - was the head - head of them, you know, and then - he had a - he had a solicitor - working for him and - and - you know, mother had to - mother rented it you see, and - she had to go into the County H
o
tel - at the time when her rent was due and - and meet this solicitor - for to pay the rent. But it was - the only snag it was - the - it - it was just a room and kitchen too you see, a wee back kitchen at - at the - open - opened the door - opened the do
