r and there was a wee back kitchen. A room and a kitchen, and - the - there was the byre, the byre was at the end - at the end of the house, and it was like - aye, whitewashed cottage with a thatched roof, thatched roof. It could be very nice you see when
 
they - when - when they started first there - they - they could work and they had a - they had a man - and - on the go that used to come and do the thatching, you know, if there was any holes or anything like that he - they - they come along and sort of t
