ke - make it all secure, and - and - put it fresh, and - and sort of - trimmed it all round about the borders and that. Oh and as time went on mother - mother looked after it you see. The - the only snag was - that the fields - the - the fields were like 
away from the house, there was fields you see - attached to it, and - and - that was the only thing, there was just one wee field - that was kind of near. And - and - mother used to - use if for - putting the cow out}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
