his road, it was quite near - in fact my sister was down for - for the - at the farms too, she come down here to be near Tinwald, and - and to be - near my father and mother. And she was in this farm, the Barbours at Tinwald Parks. And - the - so she was 
g
etting on awful grand too living there and - and she - she - she - she done - she's dead now my sister but she - she married and went away to Australia you see. But - this happened you see - that - that quick. You see, the - the - the - this car - it was 
