. So - I - this - this is just - was too late you see, there's a great big tree - great big tree, oh it was awfully big and bushy then, they said it was to come down but it never come down but they - they took some of the branches off it, it was - big hea
v
y tree. And - however I just got it. And my bicycle right over the - right over his car. I couldnae - couldnae stop you see. 'Cos he just come along that quick. And - and I landed - oh I was knocked out you see, the - I landed at - the side that you come 
out - with me - I landed - well - just for good luck I didna land - beside the dyke. If my head had struck the dyke I would have been a g}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6424897\charrsid5586003 u}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
