 the forks of my bike. What - it was - it was a big enough - kick up - it was a - and it was - an - Oc - October - I had just got my twenty - I had just got my twenty-fourth birthday past, and - that's the last day of September, and this was happening - i
n the beginning of October. And - and - so I - I got out of that - knocked out then. And then -
