d to get through that way, and - and - to get the - doctor to come, well - you see, I was unconscious and then - but they carried me - they - they lifted me into this - he had a horse and trap. And went back for his horse and trap. And then they lifted me
 
into the - lifted me off of the side of the road, and - into the trap and he brought - took me up home - took me up to my own home like. And mother got the shock of her life. When I - I landed in - carried in and - and my father you see - he was - he had 
