een away - helping - he'd been away helping some farmer, and he was just like near - nearly back - and he wasnae aw - he wasnae up like, he was resting you see, and - but however - the - mother got them to help her out of - out of this barn into the chair
 
and tell them that I was hurt and - so - when I was - they were carrying me in - the - the farmer - farmer was there too for - Barbours was there from Tinwald Parks, and he said to - to the - to them, I hope it's not - I hope she's no very - seriously inj
ured. Well, mother, she says, she's a broken leg anyway. She said, she - at least I - she can see that. She was a great spirit mother do you ken. And - and she was -
