 we did them an awful lot of harm certainly, it was a big shock for them. A bigger shock for them than what it was for me. As the doctor - as the doctor said, he says - he said, it was a frac - a fractured femur. Aye. A fractured femur you see, as well, o
n
 my left side got it for that was the side that the - where the car was coming and that was my side - that I was going down on - on the road. And I thought I was going to do all right and be at the - works at seven o'clock but I never got there at - and t
